Equivalence de rÃ¨gles:

A, B |-- C
------------- destruct H as [H0 H1].
A /\ B |-- C
--------------- intro H.
|-- A /\ B -> C


A, B |-- C
--------------- intros [H0 H1].
|-- A /\ B -> C


--------------- --------------- --------------- --------------- --------------- 

A |-- C    B |-- C
------------------ destruct H as [H0 | H1].
 A \/ B |-- C
--------------- intro H.
|-- A \/ B -> C


A |-- C    B |-- C
------------------ intros [H0 | H1].
|-- A \/ B -> C

